---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="section">
   <div class="container">
      <div class="has-text-centered mb-6">
         <h2 class="title is-2">What Our Clients Say</h2>
         <p class="subtitle is-5 has-text-grey">Hear from businesses that have found their perfect workspace</p>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-multiline">
         <div class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet">
            <div class="card testimonial-card">
               <div class="card-content">
                  <div class="media">
                     <div class="media-left">
                        <figure class="image is-48x48">
                           <img class="is-rounded" src="/images/testimonial-1.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                        </figure>
                     </div>
                     <div class="media-content">
                        <p class="title is-5">Sarah Johnson</p>
                        <p class="subtitle is-6">CEO, TechStart</p>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="content">
                     <p>"LS Professional Offices has been instrumental in our growth. The flexible terms allowed us to scale our team without worrying about long-term commitments."</p>
                     <div class="has-text-primary">
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>

         <div class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet">
            <div class="card testimonial-card">
               <div class="card-content">
                  <div class="media">
                     <div class="media-left">
                        <figure class="image is-48x48">
                           <img class="is-rounded" src="/images/testimonial-2.jpg" alt="David Chen">
                        </figure>
                     </div>
                     <div class="media-content">
                        <p class="title is-5">David Chen</p>
                        <p class="subtitle is-6">Founder, DesignHub</p>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="content">
                     <p>"The prime location and professional environment have helped us attract top talent. Our clients are always impressed when they visit our office."</p>
                     <div class="has-text-primary">
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>

         <div class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet">
            <div class="card testimonial-card">
               <div class="card-content">
                  <div class="media">
                     <div class="media-left">
                        <figure class="image is-48x48">
                           <img class="is-rounded" src="/images/testimonial-3.jpg" alt="Emily Rodriguez">
                        </figure>
                     </div>
                     <div class="media-content">
                        <p class="title is-5">Emily Rodriguez</p>
                        <p class="subtitle is-6">Director, Global Consulting</p>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="content">
                     <p>"The amenities and support services have exceeded our expectations. It's like having a full office management team without the overhead."</p>
                     <div class="has-text-primary">
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-filled" />
                        <Icon name="tabler:star-half-filled" />
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</section>

<style>
.testimonial-card {
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.media-left .image {
    margin-right: 1rem;
}

.icon {
    width: 1.2rem;
    height: 1.2rem;
}
</style>